        "id": "ocds-b5fd17-b3f725cb-5a11-4a33-9a37-e068bd48b3e0-t19029",
        "title": "Resource and Energy Efficiency Consultant Framework",
        "description": "The Business Growth Hub wishes to appoint multiple consultants to enter into a Consultancy Bank Framework Contract to support the delivery of GC BGH&#039;s Resource Efficiency Service in Greater Manchester (GM). This support will involve providing in-depth resource efficiency consultancy to selected SME manufacturing companies in GM. The bank will be made up of a small number of Resource and Energy Efficiency Consultants. \r\nThe objectives of the resource efficiency support from consultants will be to improve the competitiveness of recipient businesses through: \r\n&bull; Advising on resource efficiency including energy, water, materials and waste \r\n&bull; Identify opportunities to reduce resource consumption \r\n&bull; Recommending improving existing infrastructure or implementing new technology to increase resource efficiency \r\n&bull; Identifying opportunities to implement or utilise renewable energy sources \r\n&bull; Supporting businesses to evaluate supplier tender responses \r\n&bull; Supporting businesses to implement renewable energy and other measures resulting in achieved cost and carbon savings \r\n&bull; Supporting local SME businesses to access eligible funding and grant.\r\n\r\nThe likely value of activity under this framework for the initial project will be between &pound;40,000 and a maximum of &pound;60,000 excluding VAT.  \r\n\r\nhttps://in-tendhost.co.uk/manchestergrowthcompany/aspx/ProjectManage/79",
